snippet.title: Iron Saga VS | Pre-Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
"Alert to all Commanders! 
The Pope of Mechanical Vatican, Slokai and her drill-wielding mech Nero are approaching!
Don't be fooled by her cute appearance... she rules with an iron fist!"

Official Website: https://en.ironsagavs.com 

Iron Saga VS, the classic anime mecha 2D fighting game, reveals its final initial character: Nero! 

With robust rollback netcode and beautifully animated supermoves, rediscover your favorite mecha in Iron Saga VS, equip yourself with unique Arsenals and accomplish your heroic mission!

Official Discord server: https://discord.gg/xuXfR6e44C
Steam Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2463800/Iron_Saga_VS/
